channel.title: Look pl0xk00kar help pl0x!
channel.description:
Few things. I want to add spots to fish in the lake area by edge so what are some codes for those cuz i couldnt find them.
Also couldnt find the rock codes to mine so if someone could get them that be great. I need copper and tin and ect to rune.
Also this is a hard 1 but i want a pvp command so when i do ::pvp it makes everywhere pvp and teles every1 to edge bank when i do this and banks with be safezones( also want ::pvpoff) This is a hard 1 so i dont expect to get answer but might aswell ask...

item.title: Look pl0xk00kar help pl0x!
item.dc:creator: @marcbob marcbob
item.description:
@marcbob wrote:

[quote=“Rockin, post:2, topic:302492”][quote author=marcbob link=topic=398815.msg2959179#msg2959179 date=1253050113]
Few things. I want to add spots to fish in the lake area by edge so what are some codes for those cuz i couldnt find them.[/quote]

There are a bunch of fishing spot IDs, here’s just a few.

233, 309, 304, 800, 927, 952, 1174, 1236, 1405, 2067, 2859, 3019, 3574, 3804, 3848. You add some of those into your autospawn.cfg.

[quote author=marcbob link=topic=398815.msg2959179#msg2959179 date=1253050113]
Also couldnt find the rock codes to mine so if someone could get them that be great. I need copper and tin and ect to rune.[/quote]

I’m not 100% sure on these. 2090-2140 are the mining rock IDs. I don’t know the exact rock for each ID, test those out yourself (globalobjects).[/quote]

thanks man
